scheduler.view.view_ui
Class ListViewRow

java.lang.Object
  scheduler.view.view_ui.ListViewRow

public class ListViewRow
extends java.lang.Object

The class ListViewRow is a container of a ScheduleItem and its form as row data in the list view table. The data is modelled as a vector of objects. This class is only used within ListView.
